title: Bonus Episode - Charles Oakley talks about "The Last Enforcer"
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
NBA Legend and former New York Knicks forward Charles Oakley sat down with Ebro in the Morning to discuss his upcoming book 'The Last Enforcer'.

He discusses fighting with Charles Barkley, his relationship with Michael Jordan, Dennis Rodman's antics, and much more!
